Package oogasalad.engine.controller

Class EventConverter

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.engine.controller.EventConverter
public class EventConverter extends Object
Utility class responsible for converting EventData from the file parser into fully constructed Event objects tied to a specific GameObject.

This conversion includes parsing the event's conditions, outcomes, and type.
